ofxVectorField

A vector field generator and animator for openFrameworks.cc

- creates vector fields from existing color and grayscale images
- creates vector fields randomly using perlin noise
- animates vector fields using perlin noise
- used to animate particles

by Jeremy Rotsztain 

http://www.mantissa.ca